@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_szmetu(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v0 = (((v2 + 0.83 * tmp + 0.67) / v2) / (tmp / (tmp + 0.73 - v1 + 0.39)))
    v0 = wp.abs((wp.sin(v1 + 0.97) * (tmp + 0.26 + v0 + 0.56)))
    tmp = v2
    tmp = (0.13 / 0.74)
    tmp = v2
    tmp = wp.cos(wp.abs(tmp))
    v2 = ((wp.abs(v0 + 0.65) / (v2 + 0.39 / v1 + 0.53)) * ((tmp + 0.38 * v0 + 0.49) - v2))
    data[tid] = v0
